<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The Transform type is a base type which cannot be instantiated directly. The following concrete Transform types are available:</db:para>
<db:itemizedlist>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-rotation.xml">Rotation</db:link></db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-scale.xml">Scale</db:link></db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-translate.xml">Translate</db:link></db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-matrix4x4.xml">Matrix4x4</db:link></db:para>
</db:listitem>
</db:itemizedlist>
<db:para>The Transform types let you create and control advanced transformations that can be configured independently using specialized properties.</db:para>
<db:para>You can assign any number of Transforms to an <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-item.xml">Item</db:link>. Each Transform is applied in order, one at a time.</db:para>
</db:section>
